title: Moss Patch
description: A lush green patch of moss with a dark brown base, showcasing the vibrant texture and color of the moss.

title: Fern Plant
description: A vibrant green fern plant with multiple fronds extending upwards. The fronds are finely divided and have a lush appearance, while the base shows a cluster of roots.

title: Close-up of Fern Sori
description: A close-up image of a green fern leaf displaying multiple circular clusters of reddish-brown sori, which are structures that produce spores. The sori are arranged in a pattern along the leaf, contrasting with the vibrant green background.
